{"tid":1453749,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港經濟戰再發一炮：轉數快+買實金","createTime":"2019-08-12T05:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T03:35:59.000Z","uid":99566,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"30b8df1f782ac3a8188d59e97650f68284a0b1a8","tid":1453749,"uid":99566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:13:26.000Z","msg":"香港經濟戰再發一炮：轉數快+買實金<br />\n<br />\n店主真係好憤怒，其實一直都留定一個行動，就係睇政府痛定思痛，回應訴求，結果琴晚發生繼612、721後另一慘案。我唔能夠有招唔教，今日就同大家講點樣買金幣，亦可以達至從銀行體系結餘同貨幣供應流走抽資的效果。<br />\n<br />\n首先有4種金幣有國際統一黃金成份規格、可以係世界流通及到外地銀行換當地貨幣，風險低、帶走方便。呢4種金幣分別係楓葉金幣(加拿大)、鷹揚金幣(美國)、鴻運金幣(澳洲)、熊貓金幣(中國)。<br />\n<br />\n我苦心同各位同業、大中小企、市民求助，本文最尾就係有提供實金買賣既銀行及官網，請去銀行總行買金幣，未有戶口就同場開戶，立即準備轉數快，一開就轉錢入新戶口扣錢買金幣。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家唔想搭車去總行，請到全港各銀行直接提取現金，擺係個嘉頓什錦餅乾鐵罐存起，將來一樣有機會用，一出糧就攞現金，大家好耐無對住實體鈔票，呢幾年只係望住數字，大家應該要攞出來數下銀紙。<br />\n<br />\n呢度店主補充大家努下，金管局係6月既既數字令大家鼓舞：<br />\n香港流通貨幣現金，係6月上升93億；當中港元現金係6月上升29億；<br />\n另外港元活期存款減少161億，大家係8月請繼續努力！<br />\n金管局數字：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkma.gov.hk/media/chi/doc/key-information/press-release/2019/20190731c8a1.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkma.gov.hk%2Fmedia%2Fchi%2Fdoc%2Fkey-information%2Fpress-release%2F2019%2F20190731c8a1.pdf&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpKDV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=13fb71e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkma.gov.hk/media/chi/doc/key-information/press-release/2019/20190731c8a1.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n永亨：楓葉金幣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ocbcwhhk.com/whb/action/rate/whbRate.do?id=fc_exchange_rate_gold&amp;locale=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ocbcwhhk.com%2Fwhb%2Faction%2Frate%2FwhbRate.do%3Fid%3Dfc_exchange_rate_gold%26locale%3Dzh-hk&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpKDV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=3b21c110\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ocbcwhhk.com/whb/action/rate/whbRate.do?id=fc_exchange_rate_gold&amp;locale=zh-hk</a><br />\n中銀：楓葉金幣、熊貓金幣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bochk.com/tc/investment/rates/metal.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bochk.com%2Ftc%2Finvestment%2Frates%2Fmetal.html&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpKDV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=ccbe74c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bochk.com/tc/investment/rates/metal.html</a><br />\n招商永隆銀行：楓葉金幣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cmbwinglungbank.com/wlb_corporate/hk/personal/investments/gold-bar-and-gold-coin.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmbwinglungbank.com%2Fwlb_corporate%2Fhk%2Fpersonal%2Finvestments%2Fgold-bar-and-gold-coin.html&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpKDV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=671e31e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cmbwinglungbank.com/wlb_corporate/hk/personal/investments/gold-bar-and-gold-coin.html</a><br />\n恆生：鴻運金幣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hangseng.com/zh-hk/rates/gold-prices/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hangseng.com%2Fzh-hk%2Frates%2Fgold-prices%2F&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpKDV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=a44b9bb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hangseng.com/zh-hk/rates/gold-prices/</a><br />\n創興：楓葉金幣<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chbank.com/tc/financial/rates/gold-coin/index.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chbank.com%2Ftc%2Ffinancial%2Frates%2Fgold-coin%2Findex.shtml&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpKDV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=bc234a3c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chbank.com/tc/financial/rates/gold-coin/index.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n最後，大家要揸緊宗旨<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XgKazvhNYz8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXgKazvhNYz8&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpKDV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=cf80383b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XgKazvhNYz8</a>"},{"pid":"487905c380edf88cfe2148e778641a19bb15bef8","tid":1453749,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:16:51.000Z","msg":"推介大家去LPM買 買過唔錯"},{"pid":"6e2cdcd9f14b4d8cc384c897c983f3dade0b13b8","tid":1453749,"uid":99566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:24:23.00